+
+| Model | Allowed use | Required evidence |
+|---|---|---|
+| conditional write primitive | The store provides revision, compare-and-swap, or transactional conditional commit for the exact backend path. | Backend coverage test, conflict test, and fallback or block rule for stores that do not provide the primitive. |
